name: The Mystery v5-dv1 (Eternity Render 1)
description: The Mystery v5-dv1 was created for Feral File in 2021. This is 1 in a series of 5 renders of this digital sculpture. The Mystery is a talisman in the style of Baroque memento mori, this verison is made of ivory and gold. PNG file, 2480 x 3508 pixels
